Aging Adults:

In adults, systolic blood pressure rises from early adulthood onward, up to at least age 70. The application will automatically analyze the duration and frequency of contractions and tell you when to go to the maternity home.
Application also provides:
- Visual and voice control of breathing during labor contractions
- User friendly simulator with the basic techniques of breathing
- It can send your relatives with SMS to inform them that you need to go to maternity home after analyzing contractions  progress
- Handy log of contractions duration and frequency
- It’s possible to share with contractions  log data
